com.locuslabs.sdk.maps.view

Interface MapView.OnClickPoiListener

  • Enclosing class:
    MapView

    public static interface MapView.OnClickPoiListener
    Listener which will be called when the user has clicked on a POI on the Map

    The execute method will be called each time the user taps a POI

                   java.lang.String poiId)
